          "Review of candidate documents",
          "Conducting an interview",
          "Verification of professional skills",
          "Request for additional information"
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Employer Decision",
        "desc": "If the employer approves the candidate, the next stage begins.",
        "note": "Presenting a candidate does not mean automatic employment. The final decision is made by the employer and the relevant state authorities.",
